# PIG DICE GAME

#### This is a game of rolling dice that has engages two players who roll a dice to compete against each other , 14/05/2018

#### By **Mbiyu Ben**

## Description
The application allows two players to rival while playing a dice game.
The player who scores 100 points first wins the game.
The player rolls the dice and adds his score according to the number the dice rolled on.
However, if the player rolls number 1, he will lose all the points in his current roll.
A player can however hold his score before he rolls number 1 which makes him retain the points in the current roll.
The player who scores 100 points first wins the game.
After winning the game, the players can schoose to restart the game in order to play the game again.

## Setup/Installation Requirements
* The game has no major setup install or setup complications, just visit the link below to play.
 https://mbiyu2017.github.io/Pig-Dice/

## BEHAVIOUR DRIVEN DEVELOPMENT
BEHAVIOUR                                                INPUT                            OUTPUT
Game produces random whole numbersto number 6            roll-dice                         1 to 6
Game stores genrated number to a separate space          4                                 6
Game adds newly generated number to previous number      3 and 6                           9
Player changes role when they hold number or roll 1      Player1                           Player 2 

## Known Bugs
Application has no known bugs till now. Only switching players and restart functionalities that will be improved on.

